column2: Captain America Flying Figure & Big Head Bundle
column3:
Join the superhero ranks to save the planet with this Official Marvel Licensed Trendtimes Captain America 2CH IR RC Helicopter. Lead the cavalry into victory with this super soldier RC Helicopter and the choice of 3 distinct Heroic Action Phrases! It also features 2 channel and IR control. And it is RTF (Ready To Fly) out of the box. Assemble the Avengers, True Believer and save the world with the Trendtimes Captain America 2CH IR RC Helicopter today!

Features:

  • Officially Licensed by Marvel Comics
  • Features 3 Variant Heroic Action Phrases
  • Twin Rotors for Stability and Control
  • Ready To Fly
  • For kids 8 and up

Includes:

Introducing the Marvel Licensed Captain America 3.5 Inch Flying Figure IR UFO Big Head Helicopter! Stand for justice with this Captain America big head helicopter featuring a coaxial rotor system for precise movement and increased stability when hovering. The UFO Big Head Helicopters body is also constructed with a durable material making it strong yet lightweight so you don't have to worry about breaking anything when it lands a bit too rough. Simply turn on and launch to get started, holding your hand underneath it will keep it hovering up in the air. When done flying you can try and grab it but you can also use the included remote control to shut down and recover safely, it's that easy! A must have for fans of helicopters, get the Marvel Licensed Captain America 3.5 Inch Flying Figure IR UFO Big Head Helicopter today!

Features:

  • Marvel Licensed
  • Electric Powered
  • Durable Constructed Material
  • Easy to Fly
  • Master Hand / Eye Coordination
  • Advanced Infrared Hover Sensor Technology
  • Battery Charges with USB Charger

  • For kids ages 6 and up

column2: Envision Spy Drone
column3:
Explore and record with the Envision 2.4GHz 4.5CH Camera RC Spy Drone! This awesome RC drone has a built-in picture and video camera which you can store and save data in a 2GB memory card! The body is durable plastic and conveniently lightweight. It also has 4CH controls meaning you can fly up/down, forward/backward, strafe left/right and rotate left/right. The internal gyro means you'll always get a smooth flight. It also comes with a 2.4GHz transmitter, so radio interference won't be a problem! Enjoy recording fun fly times with friends and with the Envision Spy Drone!

column2: Captain America Helicopter Boomerang
column3:
Introducing the Helicopter Boomerang - the ultimate toy that combines the excitement of a boomerang with the thrill of a chopper flight! Crafted from soft foam for safe, endless fun, this marvel soars out an incredible 36 feet. It's as easy as child's play to send it spiraling through the air. But here's the real magic: it's self-landing!

But wait, there's more! This officially licensed Marvel masterpiece stars your favorite heroes - Spider-Man, Black Panther, Iron Man, Captain America, and Hulk - on a mission to make playtime unforgettable. Get ready to launch, catch, and relive epic adventures with the Helicopter Boomerang, where fun knows no bounds!

  • Easy to Fly
  • Master Hand / Eye Coordination

Just put in 6 AA batteries into the transmitter and charge the helicopter's rechargeable battery with the integrated charging cable on the transmitter or use the included USB Port Charger and you are good to go!
